Specification Sheet

Features

  • Color: Black(DRT3035DMN-C, DRT3035DMP-C)
  • Product Dimensions: 35 1/4" W x 32 1/8" H x 17" D(DRT3035DMN-C, DRT3035DMP-C)
  • 2015 ANSI barrier compliant
  • A newly designed pan burner
  • Dedicated rear flue configuration
  • Standard on/off and high/low flame control
  • Approved for use in any room including bedrooms
  • Clean, radiant design blend with any style of mantel or trim
  • Oak logs and glowing embers deliver elegant fire presentation
  • Add an optional ceramic fiber brick liner for a more traditional look
  • Optional wireless remote controls deliver the ultimate convenience
  • Easy access to control area without having to remove the safety barrier
  • High/Low flame operation allows you to adjust the flame intensity and heat
  • Heat-circulating design increases warm air distribution throughout the room
  • Standard IPI/CPI switch for easier operation during severe cold temperatures
  • Optional blower helps circulate warm air into a large room for maximum comfort
  • Choose from millivolt ignition system or energy saving intermittent pilot electronic ignition
  • Maximum BTU Output: 20,000
  • Min/Max Natural Inlet Pressure: 5"/10.5" WC
  • Min/Max Propane Inlet Pressure: 11"/13" WC
  • Framing Dimensions: 35 7/8" W x 36 1/4" H x 18 1/2" D
  • Venting Dimensions: 4" ID
  • Approved Direct Vent Systems: Secure Vent Direct-Vent System Components, Secure Flex Flexible Vent Components, Z-FLEX Model GA Venting Systems
  • Actual Viewing Area: 29 1/4" W x 19 1/2" H
  • Valve Type: Millivolt (Intermittent Pilot)
You're sure to be warm with the Superior DRT3000 Pro Series Top Vent Fireplace with aged Oak Logs. This fireplace comes with a natural gas or propane option as well as liner kit options of vintage red brick, buff brick, old town red brick herringbone, or black reflective porcelain. Some features of this fireplace include controls that offer energy saving pilotless ignition and a battery backup, making it dependable in power outages. In the world of fireplaces, this is definitely one worthy of purchasing. This fireplace is not only beautiful, but also efficient when it comes to heating any room.

Venting Requirements: This item requires a chimney with 4.5" inner diameter.

WARNING: For more information go to www.P65Warnings.ca.gov.
